content.description:
Sitstart howevers' clever as long as your butt is on the pad... 

  Start at the base of the arete, butt on the pad, and then climb the arete to top out over the interesting arete feature. Super fun! If your find yourself off-arete or in the green stuff you know youre doing something wrong. 

  -There is absolutely no reason to clean off any vegetation on this block, and there are no new, quality, or needed lines to be had here. Please do not brush. You will be doing an injustice to the people and access at GHSP. Thanks!-

This low block only has one boulder problem. While it could have a few others, they would be low quality, and it would require a lot of destructive cleaning... Please do not remove, clean, brush, or try to establish any other lines than the one proud arete problem that exists already on the Jetpack Block. 

  Jetpack Block is home to the tricky and enticing "Jetpack Skills Arete" which protrudes out from the rest of this small block. Once you reach the block, there is no mistaking where you climb on it.
